            <title><![CDATA[Paxton's win over Cornyn sets up high-stakes Texas clash with Talarico]]></title>
            <link>https://www.pbs.org/newshour/show/paxtons-win-over-cornyn-sets-up-high-stakes-texas-clash-with-talarico</link>
